Class GEOptions

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      com.nitrous.gwt.earth.client.api.GEOptions

public class GEOptions
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject

Used to manipulate the behavior of the Google Earth options such as, navigation, flyToSpeed, scroll wheel speed and so on.

setAutoGroundLevelViewEnabled

public final void setAutoGroundLevelViewEnabled(boolean autoGroundLevelViewEnabled)
When enabled, the view will change to 'ground level view' when the camera reaches ground level. This view provides pan and lookAt controls, but no zoom slider. The tilt will be set to 90, or parallel with level ground.

Parameters:
autoGroundLevelViewEnabled - When enabled, the view will change to 'ground level view' when the camera reaches ground level. This view provides pan and lookAt controls, but no zoom slider. The tilt will be set to 90, or parallel with level ground.
